<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Spotify Setup - Lok√©dex</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 50px auto;
      padding: 20px;
      background: #1a1a1a;
      color: #fff;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .container {
      background: #2a2a2a;
      padding: 30px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      border: 2px solid #1db954;
    }
    h1 {
      color: #1db954;
      margin-top: 0;
    }
    .step {
      background: #1a1a1a;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border-left: 4px solid #1db954;
    }
    .step h2 {
      margin-top: 0;
      color: #1db954;
    }
    code {
      background: #0a0a0a;
      padding: 2px 6px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
    }
    pre {
      background: #0a0a0a;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      overflow-x: auto;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background: #1db954;
      color: white;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin: 10px 5px;
      transition: background 0.2s;
    }
    .button:hover {
      background: #1ed760;
    }
    .warning {
      background: #ff6b6b;
      color: white;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .info {
      background: #4dabf7;
      color: white;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>üéµ Spotify OAuth Setup</h1>
    
    <div class="warning">
      <strong>‚ö†Ô∏è Important:</strong> Make sure your dev server is running before starting the OAuth flow!
      <br>Run <code>npm run dev</code> in your terminal first.
    </div>

    <div class="step">
      <h2>Step 1: Add Credentials to .env</h2>
      <p>Make sure you have these in your <code>.env</code> file:</p>
      <pre>SPOTIFY_CLIENT_ID=your_client_id_here
SPOTIFY_CLIENT_SECRET=your_client_secret_here</pre>
    </div>

    <div class="step">
      <h2>Step 2: Configure Spotify Dashboard</h2>
      <p>In your <a href="https://developer.spotify.com/dashboard" target="_blank" style="color: #1db954;">Spotify Developer Dashboard</a>, make sure your redirect URI is:</p>
      <pre>http://127.0.0.1:4321/api/spotify/callback</pre>
      <p><strong>Note:</strong> Use <code>127.0.0.1</code>, NOT <code>localhost</code> (Spotify requirement)</p>
    </div>

    <div class="step">
      <h2>Step 3: Start OAuth Flow</h2>
      <p>Click the button below to start the authorization process:</p>
      <a href="/api/spotify/auth" class="button">üöÄ Authorize Spotify</a>
      <div class="info" style="margin-top: 15px;">
        <strong>üí° Tip:</strong> Make sure you're accessing this page via <code>http://127.0.0.1:4321</code> (not localhost) 
        and that your dev server is running!
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="step">
      <h2>Step 4: After Authorization</h2>
      <p>After you authorize, you'll be redirected back and see your refresh token. Add it to your <code>.env</code>:</p>
      <pre>SPOTIFY_REFRESH_TOKEN=your_refresh_token_here</pre>
      <p>Then restart your dev server and the Spotify widget will work!</p>
    </div>

    <div class="step">
      <h2>Troubleshooting</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Connection Refused:</strong> Make sure your dev server is running (<code>npm run dev</code>)</li>
        <li><strong>Invalid Redirect URI:</strong> Check that your Spotify dashboard has <code>http://127.0.0.1:4321/api/spotify/callback</code></li>
        <li><strong>Access via 127.0.0.1:</strong> Use <code>http://127.0.0.1:4321</code> not <code>localhost</code></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>

